    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I hear that, but it seems like different groups use the term to mean different things. For example, some say the mainstream media is the one spreading fake news by pushing a certain agenda, while others say social media influencers are the problem. Do you think one side is actually more responsible for this than the other?",
