      "content": "The responsibility for the information crisis lies with the systemic failures of the modern media landscape, not just one group. Mainstream media outlets, despite their intentions, are often criticized for bias, while social media platforms have created an algorithm-driven environment that rewards sensationalism over accuracy. Ultimately, the consumer's willingness to uncritically accept information from their preferred source is the final, most critical factor.",
